{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Storage.removeItem()","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/removeItem","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API\">Web Storage API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/length\"><code>length</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/clear\"><code>clear()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/getItem\"><code>getItem()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/key\"><code>key()</code></a></li><li><em><code>removeItem()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/setItem\"><code>setItem()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Web Storage API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StorageEvent\"><code>StorageEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/localStorage\"><code>Window.localStorage</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/sessionStorage\"><code>Window.sessionStorage</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a> インターフェイスの <strong><code>removeItem()</code></strong> メソッドは、キーの名称を渡すと、指定された <code>Storage</code> からキーを削除します。指定されたキーに関連付けられた項目がない場合、このメソッドは何もしません。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>storage</var>.removeItem(<var>keyName</var>);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"keyname\"><code><var>keyName</var></code></dt>\n <dd>削除したいキーの名称を持つ <a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a>。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"返値","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/undefined\"><code>undefined</code></a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下の関数はローカルストレージに 3 個のデータ項目を作成して、 <code>image</code> データ項目を削除します。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">populateStorage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'bgcolor'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'red'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'font'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Helvetica'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'image'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'myCat.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'image'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>メモ</strong>: 実際の例として、 <a href=\"https://mdn.github.io/dom-examples/web-storage/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Storage Demo</a> をご覧ください。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webstorage.html#dom-storage-removeitem\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ja\">Storage.removeItem の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの対応","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Storage.removeItem","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage/removeItem/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API/Using_the_Web_Storage_API\">Web Storage API の使用</a></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの対応","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Storage インターフェイスの removeItem() メソッドは、キーの名称を渡すと、指定された Storage からキーを削除します。指定されたキーに関連付けられた項目がない場合、このメソッドは何もしません。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Storage.removeItem()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":